# 📦 TechStore - Full Stack E-Commerce Platform

A full-stack e-commerce web application built using **React**, **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB**, fully containerized with **Docker** and deployed on an **AWS EC2 instance** using **NGINX** as a reverse proxy.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
http://3.26.146.64

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React (Vite)
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- NGINX (for serving build)

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- JWT Authentication

### Database
- MongoDB

### DevOps / Deployment
- Docker
- Docker Compose
- AWS EC2
- NGINX Reverse Proxy

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 User authentication (Login/Register)
- 🛍️ Product listing
- 🛒 Shopping cart functionality
- 📦 REST API backend
- ⚡ Fast React frontend
- 🐳 Fully containerized setup
- ☁️ Deployed on AWS EC2

---

## 🐳 Project Architecture

```text
                    ┌────────────────────────────┐
                    │        User Browser        │
                    └────────────┬───────────────┘
                                 │
                                 ▼
                    ┌────────────────────────────┐
                    │          NGINX             │
                    │────────────────────────────│
                    │  1. Serves React Build     │
                    │  2. Reverse Proxy /api     │
                    └───────┬─────────┬──────────┘
                            │         │
                            │         │
                            ▼         ▼
                  React SPA (static)  Node.js Backend
                            │         (Express API)
                            │                 │
                            │                 ▼
                            │           MongoDB
                            │
                            ▼
                    Browser renders UI
